public abstract class HierarchicalComponent extends fr.cnrs.iees.graph.impl.TreeGraphDataNode implements CategorizedComponent, Containing<DescribedContainer<SystemComponent>>, Contained<DescribedContainer<SystemComponent>>
A class to represent containers as system components. These are TreeGraphDataNodes, ie they have children and parents through the hierarchy relation
